derline} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; color: #bc1c7d} span.s4 {font: 14.0px Helvetica} span.s5 {font: 14.0px Helvetica; color: #bc1c7d} span.s6 {font: 14.0px &#8216;Heiti SC Light&#8217;} span.s7 {font: 12.0px Arial; color: #bc1c7d} span.s8 {font: 12.0px &#8216;Heiti SC Light&#8217;} span.s9 {font: 12.0px Arial} span.s10 {color: #bc1c7d} span.s11 {font: 14.0px Arial; color: #bc1c7d}</p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span class=\"s1\"><a href=\"http://weibo.com/wangyi1973\">@<span class=\"s2\">王怡的麦克风</span></a></span>：任何人间权柄都是分割的力量，将人分为掌权者和服从者，劳心者和劳力者，统治者与被统治者。我们成为此消彼长的仇敌。但上帝的权柄是合一的力量。领受权柄和顺服权柄的人，透过属灵的权柄深深相接。就像一串糖葫芦，被串在上帝主权的恩典之上。被串起来的，都是子民，我被串在哪个位置，都是甜蜜的。</span></strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"p2\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"p2\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"p3\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span class=\"s3\"><a href=\"http://weibo.com/fuminrong\">富敏荣律师</a></span>：准备把他们培训成人民警察吗？<span class=\"s4\">&nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span class=\"s5\"><a href=\"http://weibo.com/1355725143\">@<span class=\"s6\">飞扬刘沙沙</span></a></span>：广州被捕四位民主朋友中，维权律师刘士辉、唐荆陵、作家野渡，已确认在广州公安局民警培训中心，编辑袁新亭应该也在。地址：番禺区大石镇南大路<span class=\"s4\">130</span>号。路线：公交<span class=\"s4\">211</span>大石站，地铁三号线大石站。开车从番愚大桥下从番禺大桥下去，右拐，华南培训中心前<span class=\"s4\">200</span>米路左。邮编<span class=\"s4\">511430&nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"p2\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"p6\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span class=\"s7\"><a href=\"http://weibo.com/yjzlawyer\">@<span class=\"s8\">律坛怪侠杨金柱</span></a></span>：广西四名律师涉嫌伪证罪被刑事拘留。<a href=\"http://t.cn/aKDJWQ?u=1751729431\"><span class=\"s7\">http://t.cn/aKDJWQ</span></a>据最新消息，广西北海四名律师因为涉嫌伪证罪被刑事拘留。<span class=\"s9\"> </span>该四名律师是：广西中龙律师事务所主任罗思方律师、广西青湖祥大律师事务所梁武诚律师、广西通诚律师事务所杨忠汉律师、广西百举鸣律师事务所杨在新律师。</span></strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"p2\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span class=\"s10\"><a href=\"http://weibo.com/1097414213\">袁裕来律师</a></span>：哈哈，知道了这一信息，我还真有些紧张，但不能因为紧张不说人话吧？<a href=\"http://weibo.com/n/%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7%E5%BC%A0%E9%B8%A3\"><span class=\"s11\">@</span><span class=\"s10\">人大张鸣</span></a>：有人用王立军要当中央管政法的大官来吓唬我们这些批评重庆的人，有本事辩论，有本事拿事实说话，用大官吓唬人算什么。你以为我跟你似的，见了官大的就怂？</span></strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"p7\">&nbsp;</p>\n</p>\n<p class=\"source\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;padding-right: 0px;padding-bottom: 6px;padding-left: 0px;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small\"><a href=\"http://weibo.com/e371\">@陈志军great<img class=\"small_icon vip\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t35/style/images/common/transparent.gif\" alt=\"\" /></a>：近日，大批疑似越南军人化装成我国平民，进入广西地区，在当地拆迁部门、城管部门、公安部门以及开发商部门的通力合作下，一举将他们擒获，保护了广西当地居民的生命财产安全；当地居民纷纷表示&ldquo;还是党的政策好&rdquo;、&ldquo;这是献给党的90岁生日的大礼&rdquo;、&ldquo;祝党长命百岁&rdquo;。。&nbsp;<span class=\"source_att MIB_linkbl\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;padding-right: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 18px\"><a href=\"http://weibo.com/1545094967/eCcqbyPBN9u\"><strong>原文转发</strong><strong>(939)</strong></a><span class=\"MIB_line_l\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;padding-right: 9px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 8px\">|</span><a href=\"http://weibo.com/1545094967/eCcqbyPBN9u\"><strong>原文评论</strong><strong>(262)</strong></a></span></span></strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"blogPicOri\" style=\"clear: both;text-align: center;padding: 0px;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\"></div>\n<div class=\"blogPicOri\" style=\"clear: both;text-align: center;padding: 0px;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\">\n<p style=\"padding-top: 10px;padding-right: 0px;padding-bottom: 6px;padding-left: 0px;text-align: left;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small\"><cite><a href=\"../../\"><img class=\"small_icon cls\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t35/style/images//common/transparent.gif\" alt=\"\" />收起</a> <cite class=\"MIB_line_l\">|</cite> </cite><cite><a href=\"http://ww3.sinaimg.cn/large/5c184737tw1di83y1d3j1j.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"small_icon original\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t35/style/images//common/transparent.gif\" alt=\"\" />查看大图</a> </cite><cite class=\"MIB_line_l\">|</cite> <cite><a id=\"left130820232455681209\" href=\"../../\"><img class=\"small_icon turn_l\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t35/style/images//common/transparent.gif\" alt=\"\" />向左转</a> </cite><cite><a id=\"right130820232455622931\" class=\"last_turn_r\" href=\"../../\"><img class=\"small_icon turn_r\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t35/style/images//common/transparent.gif\" alt=\"\" />向右转</a></cite></span></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small\"><img class=\"imgSmall\" src=\"http://ww3.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/5c184737tw1di83y1d3j1j.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></strong></span></div>\n<div class=\"blogPicOri\" style=\"clear: both;text-align: center;padding: 0px;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\">\n<p class=\"sms\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;padding-right: 0px;padding-bottom: 6px;padding-left: 0px;line-height: 22px;font-size: 14px;text-align: left;color: #444444;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small\"><a title=\"刘思达wisc\" href=\"http://weibo.com/sidaliu\">刘思达wisc<img class=\"small_icon vip\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t35/style/images/common/transparent.gif\" alt=\"\" /></a>：作为北京人，谢绝 //<a href=\"http://weibo.com/n/%E5%BE%90%E6%98%95\">@徐昕</a>：//<a href=\"http://weibo.com/n/%E4%BD%95%E5%85%B5\">@何兵</a>：不在家给母亲送终，却给北京人送红歌.作为北京人，谢绝.要唱红歌我自己会. //<a href=\"http://weibo.com/n/%E7%8E%8B%E5%85%B4%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%88\">@王兴律师</a>:作为首都市民，我代表自己说一句：爷不稀罕你这红歌，哪凉快哪呆着去。 //<a href=\"http://weibo.com/n/%E6%96%AF%E4%BC%9F%E6%B1%9F\">@斯伟江</a>：母亲最狠的一句话是，把歌声也献给我：到北京唱殇歌？</span></strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"MIB_assign\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 5px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;width: 474px;clear: both;color: #444444;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;padding: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\">\n<div class=\"MIB_assign_c MIB_txtbl\">\n<p class=\"source\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;padding-right: 0px;padding-bottom: 6px;padding-left: 0px;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small\"><a href=\"http://weibo.com/1413836082\">@学无止境V</a>：重庆易如国同志的母亲在去世前曾反复叮嘱他：&ldquo;娃儿，能够去北京唱红歌是全家人的骄傲，如果我走了，你也一定要去，一定要唱得漂亮，把歌声献给首都人民，也献给我。&rdquo;易如国遵从了老母亲的遗愿，尽行孝道，却遭到张鸣等一干肖小无赖的诋毁，他们根本不谈老人遗愿，断章取义，夹枪带棒，真是可耻。&nbsp;<span class=\"source_att MIB_linkbl\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;padding-right: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 18px\"><a href=\"http://weibo.com/1413836082/eCee52PlzCa\"><strong>原文转发</strong><strong>(919)</strong></a><span class=\"MIB_line_l\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;padding-right: 9px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 8px\">|</span><a href=\"http://weibo.com/1413836082/eCee52PlzCa\"><strong>原文评论</strong><strong>(777)</strong></a></span></span></strong></span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":964,"categories":[1],"tags":[17141,8872,19325,8859,15207,9378,8870,14970]}